    "questionText": "<p>If $\\mathrm{A}=\\frac{\\sin 3^{\\circ}}{\\cos 9^{\\circ}}+\\frac{\\sin 9^{\\circ}}{\\cos 27^{\\circ}}+\\frac{\\sin 27^{\\circ}}{\\cos 81^{\\circ}}$ and $\\mathrm{B}=\\tan 81^{\\circ}-\\tan 3^{\\circ}$, then $\\frac{\\mathrm{B}}{\\mathrm{A}}$ is equal to</p>\n<p>$\\_\\_\\_\\_$ .</p>",
    "options": [],
